From 1392d5d7e6832e8399a57ea9df94420e35fbc361 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Geoffrey Teale <geoffrey@teale.de>
Date: Sat, 4 Apr 2026 07:37:08 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 11/18] Guard out a weird test failure for getenv on haiku.

