From 630fce2779e03c81ca5895281064ae246c0745ef Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Geoffrey Teale <geoffrey@teale.de>
Date: Sat, 4 Apr 2026 11:20:11 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 14/18] Furher guards around tests that aren't valid for Haiku

---
